column16:
'desc': [u'

Farlin Free-drop Powder Puff (Pink) Price: Rs.210

Dusting powder on a baby’s body after bathing him or after his nappy change will keep his skin dry and free of rashes. To apply the powder evenly all over the body a powder puff is usually used. Farlin’s Free Drop Powder Puff has been designed in a very progressive way so that it gives maximum utility. A built-in powder case will allow you to deposit the baby powder into it. This will provide continuous powder without having to dip the puff in the powder every now and then.

The puff on this Farlin Free Drop is made of soft feather like fabric\xa0that will brush your bundle of joy’s skin gently and smoothly. This soft material used will control the amount of powder falling out from the powder case and thus help you in applying an even layer. With this Farlin Free Drop Powder Puff you can conveniently dust a fine layer of powder onto your darling’s body and make him feel fresh and fragrant.

column16:
'desc': [u'

Farlin Honey Soap (100 g) Price: Rs.325

Babies have delicate and tender skin that needs exceptional care to keep them healthy and free of irritations. Mild and chemical free products should be used on infant’s skin to clean and nourish them. The Farlin Transparent Soap is a mild soap that is infused with the goodness of natural ingredients such as pure honey and vegetable oil. Honey is a natural moisturizer and has antioxidants in it that will protect the skin against the harmful and adverse effects of free radicals.

This gentle soap from Farlin is suitable for giving the first bath to your darling angel. A fun filled bath with the Farlin Transparent Soap will not only help in cleansing your baby’s skin but also help you bond well with your tiny tot.
